// @mui material components
import Grid from "@mui/material/Grid";

// Soft UI Dashboard PRO React components

import DashboardNavbar from "examples/Navbars/DashboardNavbar";
import Footer from "examples/Footer";
import DataTable from "examples/Tables/DataTable";
import datatable4 from "layouts/authentication/error/datatable4";

function EditProduct() {

  return (
    <DashboardLayout>
      <DashboardNavbar />

      {/* <SuiBox p={2}>
        <Card id="profile">

            <Grid container spacing={3} alignItems="center">
              <Grid item>
                <SuiBox height="100%" mt={0.5} lineHeight={1}>
                  <SuiTypography variant="h5" fontWeight="medium">
                    Email Login Details to Clients
                  </SuiTypography>
                </SuiBox>
              </Grid>

              <Grid item xs={12} lg={6}>
                <SuiBox display="flex" justifyContent="flex-end">
                  <SuiButton variant="gradient" buttonColor="info">
                    Apply
                  </SuiButton>
                </SuiBox>
              </Grid>
            </Grid>
          </SuiBox>
        </Card>
      </SuiBox> */}

      <SuiBox my={3}>
        <SuiBox mb={3}>

            <Grid item xs={12} lg={6}>
              <SuiBox p={3}>
                <SuiTypography variant="h5">Email Login Details to Clients</SuiTypography>
              </SuiBox>

            </Grid>

            <Grid item xs={12} lg={6}>
              <SuiBox display="flex" justifyContent="flex-end">
                <SuiButton variant="gradient" buttonColor="info">
                  Apply
                </SuiButton>
              </SuiBox>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </SuiBox>

        <Card style={{ fontWeight: "bold" }}>
          <DataTable table={datatable4} entriesPerPage={false} />
        </Card>
      </SuiBox>

      <SuiBox p={2}>
        <Card id="change-password">
          <SuiBox p={3}>
            <DataTable table={datatable4} entriesPerPage={false} />
          </SuiBox>
        </Card>
      </SuiBox>

      <Footer />

export default EditProduct;
